----------------------------------------------------------------------
Purpose : J-Link script file for BCM8915x device.
          By default, only the BRCM TAP is in the JTAG chain
          which means that we have to add the Cortex-M7 by configuring the BRCM TAP.
---------------------------END-OF-HEADER------------------------------

  Jlink Commander:
  jlink.exe  -JLinkScriptFile BCM8915x.JLinkScript
  
  GDB Server:
  jlinkgdbserver -jlinkscriptfile BCM8915x.JLinkScript
 
  References:
    https://kb.segger.com/Manual_setup_of_JTAG_chain
    https://kb.segger.com/J-Link_script_files
  
*/

